Our Investment Strategy

Investing in C

Our
Big
Idea

Empowering our leaders to build our nation

Whatever the return objectives are, they ultimately have an impact on the investor. Whether it’s to help pay for a house, children’s school fees, medical care or bolster working capital for a small business. The ability to sustainably generate returns on investment ensures these goals are attained thereby impacting the client.

Through our five Pillars (Capital, Culture, Credit, City and Community), We have a platform that curates a broad array of great options that are ultimately meant to create great impact, not just for the client but for our community and nation at large. We are at the heart of creating the much-needed capital formation that would help address a lot of the infrastructure issues that continue to bedevil our development as a people.

Our Investment Strategy:
The 5 C's

Credit

According to a report by the Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN), the credit to GDP ratio in 2019 stood at a low 17.6%, which falls short of international standards. To address this issue and overcome the prevalent credit aversion in the country, we offer access to credit across multiple currencies. We provide this service not only to the government but also to businesses and individuals, enabling them to invest in a diverse range of sectors, achieve their strategic goals, and generate stable fixed returns for our clients.

Capital

One major challenge facing Nigeria is limited access to capital, due to inadequate infrastructure and limited access to financial services. This hinders national growth and economic development. To address this issue, we sustain wealth and prosperity by unlocking capital for corporations and businesses that provide goods and services for the benefit of the country. By providing them with access to financial resources, they can invest in their operations, expand their businesses, increase their workforce, and deliver improved value to their customers.

Cities

The real estate sector in Nigeria has been identified as a source of "dead capital," meaning that assets in this sector are not being utilized to their full potential. To tackle this issue, we provide financing to support the development of cities that can address the need for tradable assets and housing. Our goal is to make cities more attractive to investors, while also improving the quality of life for residents by allowing them to live more productive lives.

Communities

With the advent of technologies such as blockchain, communities are becoming empowered and small group management is becoming more feasible. As a result, we anticipate that economic power will increasingly lie within these smaller, tight-knit communities. To capitalize on this trend, we are building platforms that bring together communities of like-minded individuals and power affinity groups. By doing so, we aim to increase productivity and drive growth within these groups, ultimately contributing to the overall development of Nigeria.

Culture

Culture has the power to unify, as demonstrated by the European Renaissance where people came together to create the David statue and fostered a sense of unity in the face of war. Today, culture is arguably Nigeria's greatest export, with a thriving music, art, and movie scene that is brimming with fresh ideas. With this in mind, our aim is to create an investment platform that showcases the potential returns available in the Nigerian culture scene, including the film industry and the entire value chain. By exploring the burgeoning art scene, we hope to foster unity within the nation and help our clients tap into the rich cultural heritage of Nigeria.

Our Legacy Planning Strategy

Legacy & Estate Planning

Our estate and legacy planning services help you to preserve your values and wealth for future generations. Our expert team will work with you to develop a clear and concise estate plan that will bring your loved ones together and remove any ambiguities, resolve conflicts, and align with your overall objectives. By taking a holistic approach to estate planning, we help ensure that your legacy and wealth will continue to be passed down from one generation to the next.

Family Office Advisory

We are here to help you through life’s most challenging moments, navigate complex financial and life decisions and assisting you in leaving a legacy for the people and causes that are important to you, by creating a holistic approach and customized plan that addresses your unique needs and goals.

Wills & Trusts

Wills & Trusts is a wealth management service that helps you secure your assets for the future. In addition to creating a legal estate plan, we can also help you protect your loved ones from financial hardship in retirement--and/or provide them with income during their lifetime.

Portfolio Construction

We help you come up with an optimal bespoke porfolio that aligns with your financial goals, risk tolerance, and investment time horizon.

Global Portfolio Valuation

With the help of our Global Portfolio Valuation, our clients can quickly and completely comprehend their net worth. All of our clients' holdings across all asset classes are taken into account throughout the Global Portolio appraisal process. After that, we perform a comprehensive review of the customer's whole portfolio to determine whether the client is over or underweight in various asset classes.

Introducing

City As A Service™

Our
Big
Idea

Creating Live, Work & Play environments that enable our citizens achieve their fullest potential

We intend achieving the LOTUS- CaaS vision by providing a holistic, collaborative and curated civic experience (the City-as-a-Service) to members – individual and corporate within the Yaba Tech Ecosystem with main focus on Young Professionals with different unique location providing exceptional accommodation services and feeding into this hub which will provide a fully integrated mixed-use community for our Members

Urban Rejuvenation Projects

Lotus

Connects and embodies the commercial, retail, and housing for young professionals, symbolizing renewal and the notion of regeneration, which is consistent with our larger development strategy ethos.

Juno

Juno Community provides a social-living arrangement for Young Professionals with strong interest in the Technology Space, where we offer a curated civic experience to members – individual and corporate, with emphasis on knowledge sharing and networking amongst members

Laird Place

Laird Place is a modern development ideal for sustainable family and communal living located in Ikeja, Lagos. It is a sophisticated collection of new 2-bedroom apartments offering elegant living spaces, premium amenities, impeccable service and tranquil green spaces.

Bringing Investm​ent

Into the digital age

Our
Big
Idea

Digital Evolution of Wealth Management: Harnessing Technology to Deliver Personalized, Transparent and Data-Driven Investment Solutions

As we look to the future of investing, it's clear that technology will continue to play a central role in how we research, analyze, and make investment decisions. We expect to see more and more investors turning to alternative investments as a way to diversify their portfolios and potentially achieve higher returns. From real estate to private equity and beyond, these types of investments offer a range of opportunities for those willing to take on a little extra risk. We understand this, that is why we stay up to date with the the latest trends, building solutions to help our clients stay ahead at all times.

Tech Ventures

Wealth.ng

Wealth.ng is a streamlined investing marketplace that makes it simple to invest in assets including Treasury Bills, Savings, Agriculture, Stocks, Mutual Funds, and Real Estate.

Kada Alumni

With the aid of Kada mobile app, schools and organizations can foster stronger bonds among their members, fundraise for worthwhile causes and endowments, hold inclusive elections, and swiftly gather feedback.

Astro CX

We provide custom-made Bot management systems that address your needs in the areas of financial services, issue management, communication, and more, enabling a smooth process flow.

Ligare

Wealth as a Service - API Gateway that allows partners to integrate and consume available wealth services firms to offer services to our clients
